.SH NAME
shelly-wake - Turn device on after a delay


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBshelly wake  [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Turn a device on after a specified delay.

.PP
Useful for:
  - Waking up to lights
  - Scheduling devices to turn on
  - "Good morning" automation

.PP
Press Ctrl+C to cancel before the delay expires.


.SH OPTIONS
\fB-d\fP, \fB--delay\fP=5m0s
	Delay before turning on

.PP
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for wake


